WEBVTT

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.520
[Nega biz qumursqalarni
yemaymiz?]

00:00:09.416 --> 00:00:12.124
Asrlar davomida odamlar hasharotlarni, 
qo'ng'izlardan

00:00:12.148 --> 00:00:13.473
tortib kapalak qurti,

00:00:13.497 --> 00:00:15.351
chigirtkalar-u termitlar va

00:00:15.375 --> 00:00:18.304
ninachilargacha iste'mol qilishgan.

00:00:18.328 --> 00:00:20.449
Bu amaliyotning hatto nomi ham bor:

00:00:20.473 --> 00:00:21.488
entomofagiya.

00:00:21.512 --> 00:00:24.257
Ilk ovchilar, balki, buni
oqsillarga boy hasharotlar bilan

00:00:24.281 --> 00:00:27.370
oziqlanuvchi va ularga
ergashuvchi hayvonlardan o'rganishgandir.

00:00:28.147 --> 00:00:31.507
Biz rivojlanib, hasharotlar bizning
parhez an'analarimizga aylanganida,